leader eiichi nagasue demanded the socialists put their policy 
modifications into their platform 
yamaguchi argued it was the centrist parties turn to concede 
i think it is important for each party to have its own unique 
goals the socialist secretarygeneral said as far as policy 
modifications are concerned we did all we can do 
 
