most anyone even as some people think hes as much culprit as 
savior for the ill message he bears 
even within the administration darman past servant of six 
federal departments and four republican presidents is the white 
house insider everyone loves to hate by the halfserious account 
of other cabinet officers he is an unreformed scrooge one who 
arises from his nocturnal visions ready to turn not his own but 
somebody elses leaf 
drug czar william bennett put it this way last month its 
