united airlines pilots flight attendants and machinists 
outlined their employee stock ownership proposal in a letter 
wednesday to parent company uals board which is meeting today 
the letter offered few details of the plan nevertheless the 
development marks a distinct change in attitude on the part of the 
machinists union whose opposition to employee ownership and 
