of the companies and their us subsidiaries 
it alleges that matsushita electric industrial co ltd and its 
panasonic division victor co of japan ltd and its jvc corp 
subsidiary sanyo electric co ltd sony corp nec corp sharp 
corp and sanyo electric co ltd tried to monopolize markets and 
prevent introduction of govideos vcr2 
the defendants did not immediately respond 
